PrecisEnactment of the NORTH BATTLEFORD AIRPORT ZONING REGULATIONS which place the usual limits on the height of new and existing structures and objects of natural growth, and prohibit the disposal of waste attractive to birds within a four-kilometre radius of North Battleford Airport in Saskatchewan.
